{"tid":2312706,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"月費15元無廣告「買返自由值得」","createTime":"2020-12-05T07:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T16:02:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59667d39a7a31326e5e3c138b733867559b46eaa","tid":2312706,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:40:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/NNAXC3IHM5B6TDRIHJA2SL3Q3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FNNAXC3IHM5B6TDRIHJA2SL3Q3Y%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w0v%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=496f6932\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FNNAXC3IHM5B6TDRIHJA2SL3Q3Y%2F&h=6db4fbf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201202/NNAXC3IHM5B6TDRIHJA2SL3Q3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n月費15元無廣告「買返自由值得」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YkOCogbvxvEVNXo-SMSVsCJcxcc=/1773x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FA45O3HPOVBAZN2QHK7AD5LTWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYkOCogbvxvEVNXo-SMSVsCJcxcc%3D%2F1773x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFA45O3HPOVBAZN2QHK7AD5LTWY.jpg&h=84a8dbd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Tim認為fb不斷打壓黃店，有必要增設新渠道。<br />\n<br />\n在介面與功能方面，MeWe亦與facebook十分相似，可以在個人頁面分享文字、相片或影片，同樣設有Timeline集中顯示朋友、專頁的帖文，用戶可以自由加入不同的群組，並在各群組專屬聊天室即時交流。但由於MeWe標榜無廣告，營運開支主要靠月費維持，因此要更大的儲存相片空間或是啟用自定義功能，就要成為付費會員，連原來在facebook免費提供的專頁服務，每個月就要1.99美元（約15.42港元）。雖然要收錢，但有人卻對此甘之如飴。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港人轉投MeWe擺脫fb金剛箍  黃店群組大增 力保言論自由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n單靠Hashtag吸千粉絲<br />\n<br />\n「用呢個價錢，買返自己嘅言論自由，係值得㗎囉。」今年創業成立海外速遞服務LHK Express及雜貨網店「日常Daily」的Tim，眼見facebook上的黃店不斷被打壓，認為有必要增設新渠道與顧客保持聯繫，成為首批在MeWe開設專頁的黃店之一，想不到單靠Hashtag，兩個專頁已分別吸引逾千人「追蹤（Follow）」，認為宣傳的效果較facebook更佳，「facebook你唔落廣告，你嘅hit rate係好低，我亦都唔想再畀佢賺」，而且平台以同路人為主，勝在同聲同氣，「作為一間黃店啦，都希望起到個帶頭作用」。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員、浸大政治及國際關係學系前助理教授黃偉國，2007年開始使用facebook，見證這間互聯網巨頭，由本來只是朋友間聯繫的工具，發展到今日能主宰大家生活。。。。。。。。。。。。。。佢行嘅每一步，可能都令到某啲網民不滿，大家就會反應離場」。"},{"pid":"18261711953e009366e58e0e5b4b80b47679a9ff","tid":2312706,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"港人轉投MeWe擺脫fb金剛箍  黃店群組大增 力保言論自由<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2312060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2312060</a>"},{"pid":"6f6b0b90e828e3692342f0da5d8c32e998ca8cda","tid":2312706,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0cf1d193da8e7cb942a2fa531fd1d5b2b937f8","tid":2312706,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:02:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}